      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has served as a reliable daily driver. It has been consistently well-maintained, with the engine running smoothly and all major mechanical systems functioning exactly as they should. While the car shows some minor signs of normal use, such as small stone chips on the hood and slight wear on the driver's seat bolster, the interior is clean and smoke-free. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a well-cared-for vehicle that is ready for the road.",
